     <h2>
      <a href="/">
       mnmlst
      </a>
      :
      <b>
       ‘I cld nvr gv p’
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       I’v fnd tht whn I tlk bt smplfyng r mnmlsm n gnrl, ppl r gnrlly pstv … bt whn y gt dwn t spcfcs, thy’r nt lwys s nthsstc.
      </p>
      <p>
       Whn I tlk bt gvng p nncssry shppng r clths r shs, mny ppl blk. Whn I tlk bt gvng p  cr, r gttng  smllr hm, r nt drnkng sgry cff drnks, r gvng p jnk fd … I lwys hr  lt f ppl wh sy, “I’d lv t b  mnmlst, bt I cld nvr gv p my ____.” (Y cn fll n th blnk.)
      </p>
      <p>
       I thght th sm thng, mny tms, whn I’d hr bt thr ppl mkng chngs. “I cld nvr gv tht p,” I thght t myslf.
      </p>
      <p>
       I ws wrng.
      </p>
      <p>
       I sd I cld nvr gv p my hmbrgrs r frd chckn, bt nw I’m  vgtrn.
      </p>
      <p>
       I sd I cld nvr gv p my cbl
       <span class="caps">
        TV,
       </span>
       bt I’v bn wtht t fr 6 r 7 yrs nw.
      </p>
      <p>
       I sd I cld nvr gv p my cgrtts, bt I’v bn tbcc-fr fr nrly 5 yrs.
      </p>
      <p>
       I sd I cld nvr gv p my swts, nd nw I nly hv  fw bts nw nd thn.
      </p>
      <p>
       I sd I cld nvr gv p my cr, bt I brly drv nw nd m gng cr-fr nxt mnth.
      </p>
      <p>
       I sd I cld nvr gv p pckgd fds, bt nw I lmst nly t rl fd, npckgd.
      </p>
      <p>
       I sd I cld nvr gv p my cff, bt I rcntly hv.
      </p>
      <p>
       I sd I cld nvr gv p my rnnng shs, bt nw I rn brft.
      </p>
      <p>
       I sd I cld nvr gt dwn t  hndfl f clths, bt I hv.
      </p>
      <p>
       I sd I cld nvr gv p TV ltgthr, bt I m.
      </p>
      <p>
       If y thnk y cld nvr d smthng … stp syng t. Y jst mght srprs yrslf.
      </p>
